re-ACK 8d5994e modulo question at https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/17487#discussion_r433961320, reviewed changes since my previous review per `git diff 8bb1163 8d5994e` and verified that this builds cleanly on Debian gcc and clang locally with the works.


<details><summary>Changes since last review at 8bb1163</summary><p>

```diff
$ (pr/17487)$ git diff 8bb1163 8d5994e
